<para>Example usage:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".dts"><codeline><highlight class="normal">&amp;spi1<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>cs-gpios<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;&amp;pmod0<sp/>PMOD_SPI_CS<sp/>GPIO_ACTIVE_LOW&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>example_device:<sp/>example-dev@0<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>compatible<sp/>=<sp/>&quot;vnd,spi-device&quot;;</highlight></codeline>
